---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Company Retreats & Remote Team Offsites in Thailand" 
  description="End-to-end tailored company retreats, executive planning trips, and remote team meetups across Thailand."
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-20">
    
    <header class="pt-10 mb-8" transition:animate="fade">
      <span class="text-xs font-mono tracking-widest uppercase text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 mb-4 block">
        // Real-world operational logistics
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl mb-6 font-black tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white leading-[1.1]">
        Stop micro-managing <br />
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 dark:from-blue-400 dark:to-cyan-300">
          your team's retreats.
        </span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        I serve as Project Director for Offsite Thailand. Backed by Ace Marketing Solutions and Boutiq Thailand, my team builds end-to-end custom itineraries so distributed software companies can gather in person without the logistical headaches.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="mb-12 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800/60 shadow-md" transition:animate="fade">
      <img 
        src="/images/offsite.jpg" 
        alt="Offsite Thailand — Team retreat operations on location" 
        class="w-full h-[280px] sm:h-[380px] md:h-[480px] object-cover transition-all duration-700 ease-out"
        loading="eager"
        decoding="async"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 py-6 mb-12 border-y border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800/60" transition:animate="fade">
      <div>
        <span class="block text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">30+ Years</span>
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Combined Hospitality Exp</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="block text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">100% Custom</span>
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Zero Fixed Templates</span>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-2 md:col-span-1">
        <span class="block text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">End-to-End</span>
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Ground Operations</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-3xl mb-16 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300" transition:animate="fade">
      <p>
        Bringing globally distributed teams together shouldn't feel like an administrative nightmare. Most companies waste weeks arguing over hotel choices, diet configurations, airport ground routes, and venue spacing constraints. 
      </p>
      <p>
        We built Offsite Thailand to run like a clean software deployment. We handle the entire stack manually—sourcing secure local venues, coordinating regional transit lanes, managing complex allergy requirements, and locking down dedicated meeting infrastructure. 
      </p>
      <p>
        This isn't generic event planning. It's high-touch hospitality tailored for tech operators who need to jump straight from strategic product roadmapping to local cultural excursions without missing a beat.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="py-12 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800/60" transition:animate="fade">
      <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-mono text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 mb-8">
        // Core Retreat Tracks
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-8 mb-12">
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Company Retreats</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Full-scale corporate infrastructure setup. We blend team activities, comfortable accommodation layouts, and regional venue logistics for large international scaleups.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-1">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Executive & Leadership Retreats</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            High-tier environments designed for heads of engineering and founders. Premium private spacing focused on deep strategic roadmapping, wellness, and isolation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-1">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Remote Workforce Meetups</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Bringing asynchronous teams face-to-face for the first time. We design schedules balancing deep work blocks with natural, unforced local connection loops.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-1">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Team Building & Culture</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Expert-led field challenges, workshops, and excursions designed to test problem-solving without the awkward corporate icebreaker clichés.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-12 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800/60" transition:animate="fade">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-mono text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 mb-2">
          // Footprint Nodes
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-xl">
          We source and execute ground programs natively across Thailand’s most stable infrastructure networks.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-y-4 gap-x-8 text-sm font-mono text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
        <div>📍 Chiang Mai <span class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 font-normal text-xs block md:inline-block md:ml-1">// Mountain Hub</span></div>
        <div>📍 Phuket <span class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 font-normal text-xs block md:inline-block md:ml-1">// Coastal Networks</span></div>
        <div>📍 Bangkok <span class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 font-normal text-xs block md:inline-block md:ml-1">// Urban Logistics</span></div>
        <div>📍 Pattaya <span class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 font-normal text-xs block md:inline-block md:ml-1">// Coastal Access</span></div>
        <div>📍 Hua Hin <span class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 font-normal text-xs block md:inline-block md:ml-1">// Executive Enclaves</span></div>
        <div>📍 Chiang Rai <span class="text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 font-normal text-xs block md:inline-block md:ml-1">// Remote Isolation</span></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-12 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800/60" transition:animate="fade">
      <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-mono text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 mb-8">
        // The Delivery Pipeline
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-xs font-mono">
        <div class="p-5 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800/60">
          <div class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold mb-2">01 / Scope</div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Briefing call to map out team scale, engineering goals, and cultural pacing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800/60">
          <div class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold mb-2">02 / Estimate</div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Comprehensive cost breakdown itemizing rooms, transit networks, and menus.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800/60">
          <div class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold mb-2">03 / Refine</div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Adjust resort layers, inject technical specs, and lock down workshop blocks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-lg bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-800/60">
          <div class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 font-bold mb-2">04 / Deploy</div>
          <p class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Your remote team arrives. Our on-the-ground operators manage the schedule.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-zinc-900 border border-slate-100 dark:border-zinc-800 rounded-xl p-8 text-left mt-8" transition:animate="fade">
      <div class="max-w-xl mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Ready to brief our planners?</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Skip the standard web contact templates. Send over your group size, target travel dates, and spatial requirements directly to my operations email.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <a 
        href="https://offsitethailand.com/" 
        class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-5 py-3 rounded-md text-sm font-bold no-underline hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors"
      >
        Let's Plan Your Next Retreat
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>